author: Journal Inquirer Staff
title: GIRLS SWIMMING
text:
GIRLS SWIMMING By Journal Inquirer Staff Journal Inquirer | 0 comments 
East Catholic 91, South Windsor 88 
Maddie Crowley (200 freestyle, 100 butterfly) and Shannon Leary (500 freestyle, 100 breaststroke) were double winners for East Catholic as it topped South Windsor. The Eagles also got wins from Shelby Caron (50 freestyle), Kelly Chmielewski (100 freestyle), and Sarah Stevenson (diving). Sam Dickinson, Gabby Caron, and Maggie Hallisey also starred. 
Elizabeth Savidge (200 IM) and Kate Niemiec (100 backstroke) won for South Windsor. East Catholic is at E.O.
